snippet.title: BlazBlue Series Rollback Netcode Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Rollback Netcode for BlazBlue Centralfiction and BlazBlue Cross Tag Battle!
Check out the message from BlazBlue Series Producer Toshimichi Mori!
The Open Beta is currently going for BlazBlue Centralfiction be sure to participate!
